title: Dario Argento's Phenomena - 1985
description:
"A young girl, with an amazing ability to communicate with insects, is transferred to an exclusive Swiss boarding school, where her unusual capability might help solve a string of murders." - IMDB 

 This is the german edition disc, ripped and rebuilt into NTSC format.  The english soundtrack is available but plays with german subs.  Just disable subtitles on your DVD player and problem is solved.
